'''''Mimban Cloudrider''''' was one of the [[Bacta Tanker]]s [[Raid on Thyferran Convoy Delta-Two-Niner|captured]] by [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] during the [[Bacta War]]. It was later used to insert covertly [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]], [[Elscol Loro]], [[Sixtus Quin]], [[Mirax Terrik Horn|Mirax Terrik]], and [[Iella Wessiri Antilles|Iella Wessiri]] in [[Thyferra/Legends|Thyferra]]. They were disguised as the ships's crew under various pseudonyms and their mission was to make contact with the [[Ashern]] faction.

